result.adr_address: 30 Cochrane St, Central, Hong Kong
result.name: Ser Wong Fun

reviews.text: Well maintained place with middle to upper range price. Not really value for money but the food is good enough for the calories quota for the day. The better alternative will be 蛇王二 at Causeway Bay. Almost the exact menu and much tastier, better value for money.

I will be honest, the snake soup is good if no one say, it does have some game taste but does not really taste like one.

The lotus root with pork n chestnut in a patty is very good. The liver n pork sausage is not too oily n taste nice

Apart from the snake soup, the goose and the blood liver sausage was quite good too. The snake soup is quite heavy in taste, hard to describe, something like a very sharp gamey taste. Worth a try, I probably won’t have it again though. But if there’s one place to experience this, this restaurant will be it!

Snake soup 4/5
Other food 2/5
Price 1/5
Service 1/5
Definitely not a cozy place to eat
Poor quality

result.adr_address: 香港中環閣麟街30號
result.name: 蛇王芬

reviews.text:
如果評分是可以是負星或以下，我會毫不猶豫地給予蛇王芬的，請想到訪的食客細看：
1. 先評招牌所註明的蛇~蛇羹，湯羹稀薄沒有味道，像湯水一般，蛇肉有刺去不乾淨，整碗喝完後，沒有暖胃禦寒功效，每碗收費$140，脆片給得小氣到只有兩片，菊花欠奉，負分實至名歸。
2. 滑雞膶腸煲仔飯，每吃一口都想罵髒話，請問斬雞的師父，你學滿師了嗎？會用刀嗎？學會斬好一隻雞嗎？雞塊斬到不倫不類，不三不四，每塊都給你斬到吃時骨頭刺破嘴，還帶有碎骨，結果碎骨就掉到飯裡，你覺得這還有得評分嗎？
3. 如果烹調功夫出眾到家，在這地段收費高點是合理的，但憑以上廚師功夫，請認真考慮減價或改善廚藝才在中環獻醜。

Well maintained place with middle to upper range price. Not really value for money but the food is good enough for the calories quota for the day. The better alternative will be 蛇王二 at Causeway Bay. Almost the exact menu and much tastier, better value for money.
食物有水準，只差坐位不太舒服
冬天會難找到坐位，比一般餐廳多些選擇

result.adr_address: 30 Cochrane St, Central, Hong Kong
result.name: Ser Wong Fun 蛇王芬

reviews.text: Snake soup is a chicken meat soup. Taste neutral. Duck liver is inside a sausage however nit easy to recognize and taste very weird. Fried rice with beef was nice and the best of those 3 dishes. Will never come back regardless of price. I feel they cheat about ingredients...

A tradition Hong Kong Styled restaurant serving good quality snake soup. The menu is good and you can saving a lot. Everything is good but the staff is expecting to finish your meal as soon as you can since a long queue is always existing
Snake soup was above average. Not sure if they use chicken meat as a filler in their soups. Other dishes were average at best.
Snake soup. Needless to say it tastes like fish. Pricey, but unique and they even show us ignorant westeners how it should be eaten.
Ordinary food. Snake soup was ok

result.adr_address: 香港中環閣麟街30號
result.name: Ser Wong Fun 蛇王芬

reviews.text: 超正干炒牛河、原盅懷舊燉湯、有人情味老闆娘、果皮綠豆沙……

Snake soup is a chicken meat soup. Taste neutral. Duck liver is inside a sausage however nit easy to recognize and taste very weird. Fried rice with beef was nice and the best of those 3 dishes. Will never come back regardless of price. I feel they cheat about ingredients...
非常失望，舊年去過D出品是可以。今天晚上去蛇羮竟然有餿味 ，老闆試過味之後就同我哋換過哂D蛇羮，但之後發現D蛇羮係冇蛇肉，其餘的小菜一點都不吸引。

香港で初めての夕食はこのお店と言う事で連れてきてもらいました。

このお店の特徴のメニューは何といっても、店名にも付いている「蛇」です。そう蛇を材料にしたメニューがあるのです。

自分が食べたのは蛇を薬草などとともに長時間炊き込んだスープです。

小さめのどんぶりに並々と、そして上には上げたワンタンの皮が乗っています。
　蛇と言う事ですが食感や味は鶏肉に来ている感じですが、少し癖があるような、でも薬草などと一緒に煮込んでいるせいかあまり気になりません。

　追加で、鶏肉とタロイモのココナッツミルク煮、カモのローストなどを注文。さらに白米も注文し香港の夜はガッツリ地元の人たちが行くお店で堪能することが出来ました。

真材實料的燉湯和美味蛇𡙡，最愛古法煲仔飯丶潤腸和生炒糯米飯，紮實的粵菜味道很好，不防一試。
意外發現燒鵝非常好吃😋，大家一定要吃陳皮綠豆沙。
冬天要排隊等候，提議先訂位。
